	)
	(text "i fully intend to hack on a \"high speed\"\nisa slot for use with fpga video cards while\nstill maintaining full PC AT compatibility\n~8mhz low speed and cpu bus clock x1 or x0.5 could be high speed"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 139.446 760.222 0)
		(effects
