	(text "v2 changes:\n- got rid of 595 shift regiser DMA/DACK output system for more fpga pins\n- fixed the dram_WE line, exchanged for PIC_1_en. interrupts will have to be none-8259 compatible\n- seperate CKE0 line to dram\n- spi roms actually have spi ports now\n- fixed missing spi_vcc\n- attempt to make it possible for the fpgas to run system without i486\n- fixed dram high word latches so they're no longer backwards"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 1032.764 710.692 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "19fb36be-a6a6-4996-8c91-fd4c9c346d3e")
	)
	(text "molex power connectors:\nhttps://www.digikey.com/en/products/detail/te-connectivity-amp-connectors/1586515-2/808592"
