	(text "the \"for real\" 486. (the one before this worked, making this a second version or something)\nfeatures:\n-16 bit isa bus\n-32 bit ram bus. sram and also dram. dram has a 64 but bank swapping system to make contiguous 32 bit reads faster\n-2 ice40 fpgas. 32 bit to 16 bit isa bus steering needs a lot of pins (60+)\n-make the second fpga also do dma and interrupts for ms-dos compatibility\n-verilog code to enable a spi rom based bios is still in development, so a parallel rom is still required"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 1069.594 804.672 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "868cdf8d-b894-4871-94a2-94b4969fe571")
	)
